title: Adalat
subTitle: Dharma leaves his village and moves to Mumbai to lead a better life. However, things take an ugly turn when the police suspects his connection in a criminal case and arrests him.

title: Anamika
subTitle: A writer rescues an injured woman who suffers from memory loss but claims to be his wife. In the process of finding out her real identity, he falls in love with her.

title: Amir Garib
subTitle: Mohanlal, a musician and a thief, robs rich people and distributes the money amongst the poor. However, things take a turn when he falls for Sunita, a wealthy man's daughter.

title: Baadshah
subTitle: An amateur detective, Raj, goes by the nickname of Baadshah. But this name soon causes a misunderstanding that lands him in the middle of a conspiracy to assassinate the chief minister of Goa.

title: Khoon Ki Pukaar
subTitle: A compassionate pujari, Vidya, shelters a maimed bandit, unaware of his hidden motives. Subsequently, Vidya must confront a moral dilemma that could change their lives forever.

title: Shirdi Ke Sai Baba
subTitle: A doctor who does not believe in Sai Baba's powers travels to Shirdi with his ill son. Soon, the doctor has to decide between Sai Baba and science to treat his ailing son.

title: Jeevan Mrityu
subTitle: Upon his release from exile, Ashok's life turns upside down when he learns about his mother's death and the truth behind his false accusation.

title: Pyar Jhukta Nahin
subTitle: Ajay and Preeti's marriage succumbs to misunderstandings sown by a disapproving patriarch. However, their hearts remain loyal to one another even after enduring years of separation.

title: Dacait
subTitle: After being mercilessly beaten and abandoned to die, a young man is rescued by a band of dacoits, who nurse him back to health in their hidden lair.

title: Sheshnaag
subTitle: Pritam and Banu, two shape-shifting snakes in human form, seek protection from a young man when an evil priest tries to hunt them down and use them in a ritual for wealth and immortality.

title: Sheshnaag

title: Keemat
subTitle: Sudha goes undercover on Gopal's instructions to put an end to a human trafficking business that abducts young women. But they are unaware that the assignment is compromised and poses a grave risk.

title: My Life My Story
subTitle: The host invites prominent Bollywood celebrities who open up about their personal life and share interesting anecdotes based on their experiences.

title: Chandan Ka Palna
subTitle: Ajit's perfect marriage to Shobha turns upside down after she starts behaving strangely with him and his mother, leading to a disturbed life.

title: Hum Paanch
subTitle: Thakur Vir Pratap Singh, a landlord, rules over a town with an iron fist and crushes anybody who opposes him. However, unable to put up with his atrocities, five men join hands to destroy him.

title: Upkar
subTitle: Radha's elder son sacrifices his ambitions to ensure his brother Puran gets a good education. Despite this, Puran grows up to become a ruthless man.

title: Purab Aur Paschim
subTitle: Bharat, a freedom fighter's son, travels to England to study and strives to change the mindset of the people there towards India.

title: Desh Premee
subTitle: Master Dinanath's life crumbles after he helps arrest Thakur Pratab Singh. Estranged from his wife and daughter, he relocates to a slum with his son Raju, who tragically falls into a life of crime.

title: Kranti
subTitle: Sanga, a devout employee of Raja Laxman Singh, is falsely accused of killing him. He escapes prison and forms a group of revolutionaries with the sole aim of driving the British out of India.

title: Hum Hindustani
subTitle: The Nath family faces hard times because of a property dispute. Things come to a head when one of the sons in the family is accused of theft.

title: Anita
subTitle: When Anita commits suicide, Neeraj suspects foul play and decides to investigate the truth. However, things take a turn when he starts seeing Anita everywhere.

title: My Life My Story
subTitle: The host invites prominent Bollywood celebrities who open up about their personal life and share interesting anecdotes based on their experiences.

title: Izzat
subTitle: Constable Ram Chandra teaches his son Siddharth to be a diligent policeman and lead his life with honesty and dignity. Siddharth follows his advice until circumstances force him to leave his ideals.

title: Classic Legends
subTitle: Host Javed Akhtar presents the lives and careers of the greatest personalities of the golden era of Bollywood, as a tribute to their work.

title: Woh 7 Din
subTitle: Anand, a doctor, realises that Maya, his wife, loves someone else but married him out of coercion. Thus, he sets out to reunite the lovers, but they don't want to be together anymore.

title: Baseraa
subTitle: Nima and Balraj's life is thrown out of gear when her sister and Balraj's first wife, Sharada, returns home after spending 14 years in a mental asylum.

title: Singhasan
subTitle: When the kingdoms Avanti and Gandharva are attacked by the enemies, the commander in chief of the latter decides to outwit everyone else.

title: Khatron Ke Khiladi
subTitle: Balwant, a truck driver, is driven into the underworld as he wants to take revenge on the owners of the trucking company for the death of his brother.

title: Andaz
subTitle: Sheetal, a widow, is a school teacher and lives with her son after her husband's death. She meets her student's father Ravi, a widower, and decides to marry him.

title: Saagar
subTitle: Raja secretly loves Mona, but she is in love with Ravi. However, Ravi's grandmother disapproves of their relationship and asks Mona to forget him and marry someone else.
